{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.400", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.800", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.760", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lernenden wird h\u00e4ufig erz\u00e4hlt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.640", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wiederholt es noch einmal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.280", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann pr\u00e4gt es sich besser ein.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.240", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gleiches hat sich wohl die Gro\u00dfe Koalition mit ihrer Skizze vom Chancenland Deutschland gedacht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.840", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber eines vorab: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.880", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Je \u00f6fter die Gro\u00dfe Koalition das deutsche Bildungssystem als Faktor zur \u00dcberwindung von sozialer Ungerechtigkeit betrachtet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.120", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "umso \u00f6fter verkennt sie auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.080", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es Ungerechtigkeit produziert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.240", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nach den Ausf\u00fchrungen von Frau Karliczek zu den Vorhaben der Bundesregierung im Bereich Bildung muss ich doch einige kritische Anmerkungen machen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.000", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erstens: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.560", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Kooperationsverbot. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.600", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir Linke haben einen Antrag in das Verfahren eingebracht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.840", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der bisher durch die Gro\u00dfe Koalition immer wieder verschoben und vertagt wurde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.600", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Offensichtlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.640", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.320", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben Sie Angst, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.000", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dieser Antrag hier eine Mehrheit findet."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.160", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Linke will eine Aufhebung des Kooperationsverbotes ohne Einschr\u00e4nkungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.920", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bildung muss endlich als eine wirkliche Gemeinschaftsaufgabe von Bund und L\u00e4ndern verstanden werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.160", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das nennt man dann kooperativen Bildungsf\u00f6deralismus."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.160", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zweitens: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.960", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Ganztagsschulen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.720", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es stellt sich die Frage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.440", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob sich der Bund beim Ausbau von Ganztagsschulen im Sekundarbereich aus der Verantwortung stehlen oder nur Kosten sparen will, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.760", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem er sich auf den Primarbereich beschr\u00e4nkt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.000", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ehemalige Ganztagsschulprogramm, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.760", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das bis 2009 galt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.760", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "umfasste damals 4\u00a0Milliarden Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.440", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im jetzigen Koalitionsvertrag will man mit der H\u00e4lfte auskommen und das bei einem deutlich gestiegenen Bedarf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.000", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das wird nicht funktionieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.960", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Linke fordert einen Rechtsanspruch auf Ganztagsbetreuung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.840", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht nur in der Grundschule."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.320", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Den gro\u00dfen Fachkr\u00e4ftebedarf bei den Kolleginnen und Kollegen an den Grundschulen will ich zumindest benennen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.600", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese schmerzliche L\u00fccke wird in den n\u00e4chsten sieben Jahren auf \u00fcber 100\u00a0000\u00a0Kolleginnen und Kollegen anwachsen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.760", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit dieser Herausforderung d\u00fcrfen wir die L\u00e4nder nicht alleinelassen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.680", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen dringend mehr Personal in der Bildung: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.880", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schulsozialarbeiter, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.520", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lehrkr\u00e4fte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.800", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schulpsychologen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.200", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn nur in einem guten Team kann gute P\u00e4dagogik funktionieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.960", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drittens: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.560", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die berufliche Bildung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.360", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Koalitionsvertrag findet sich dazu au\u00dfer Lippenbekenntnissen leider nicht viel. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.320", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Grundlegende Probleme werden nicht angegangen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.240", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Au\u00dferdem dr\u00fcckt sich die Koalition um die Frage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.200", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie die mittlerweile knapp 2\u00a0Millionen jungen Menschen im Alter von 20 bis 34\u00a0Jahren ohne abgeschlossene Berufsausbildung eine voll qualifizierende Ausbildung erhalten k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.160", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch hier gibt es keine verbindlichen Festlegungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.400", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Linke will eine solidarische Umlagefinanzierung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.080", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die alle Betriebe f\u00fcr die Ausbildung junger Menschen in die Pflicht nimmt und eine Mindestausbildungsverg\u00fctung erreicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.000", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es g\u00e4be noch andere Themen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.640", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "fehlender Wille der Bundesregierung zur wirklichen Inklusion, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.840", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die teils schlechten Arbeitsbedingungen und L\u00f6hne von P\u00e4dagoginnen und P\u00e4dagogen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.440", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Abschlie\u00dfend, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.120", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.280", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.760", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sage ich: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.040", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es muss in der Bundesrepublik Deutschland endlich Schluss damit sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.320", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sch\u00fclerinnen und Sch\u00fcler im 21.\u00a0Jahrhundert mit einem Unterricht aus dem 20.\u00a0Jahrhundert und einem Bildungssystem aus dem 19.\u00a0Jahrhundert konfrontiert werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.800", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danke sch\u00f6n."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.840", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt erteile ich der Kollegin Dr.\u00a0Dietlind Tiemann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.520", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "CDU/CSU-Fraktion, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.280", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ebenfalls zu ihrer ersten Rede im Deutschen Bundestag das Wort."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.640", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bitte die Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.920", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die im Saal sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.400", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Platz zu nehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.600", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jeder Redner hat Anspruch darauf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.000", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass er geordnet vortragen kann."
   ]
  }
 ]
}